description: Client tool for ingesting data into Kusto service.
releaseNotes:
12.3.0:
        ### Added
        * Added support for AzCli authentication.
        * To use AzCli against blob storage, set 'ConnectToStorageWithUserAuth' to 'AZ_CLI'.
        * To use AzCli against Kusto, set 'azCli' to true (default is false).
        ### Fixed
        * use dotnet tool with .net framework 8
title: Microsoft.Azure.Kusto LightIngest
